<p>
  Select a Phone Number<br/>
  Subscribers can text a keyword to this number to subscribe to your text notifications,
  call this number to subscribe to your voice notifications and
  you may use it as a text comment line in which you can communicate with your customers!
</p>

<div class="row alignleft">
  <label><strong>Enter Area Code</strong></label>
  <%= text_field_tag :area_code, "", :class => "inputtext input_middle required" %>
</div>

<div class="space"></div>

<div class="row alignleft">
  <label><strong>Select Phone Number</strong></label>
  <%= text_field_tag :number, "", :class => "inputtext input_middle required" %>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div>

<br/>

<p>
  What if I want to use a short code like 41257 instead?<br/>
  You will have that option on the dashboard once you create an account.
  For now, please select a phone number (they are free and you don't have to use it
  if you don't want to).
</p>


<%= hidden_field_tag :step_id, "2" %>

<div class="row alignleft">
  <%= link_to "BACK", register_user_path(:step_id => "1"), :class => "btn-submit btn-link" %>
</div>

<div class="space"></div>

<div class="row alignleft">
  <%= f.submit "NEXT", :class => "btn-submit" %>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div>